# VideoDuplicateCheck

Windows-focused Python desktop tool for finding duplicate or near-duplicate videos by content fingerprints.

## Features

- Recursive directory scan for common video formats
- Video metadata + frame-level perceptual hashing (dHash + pHash)
- Similarity threshold for exact and near-duplicate grouping
- SQLite cache for incremental scans
- Duplicate grouping with keep recommendation (resolution/bitrate/size)
- Batch operations: move or delete files
- Export report to CSV or JSON

## Quick start

```bash
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m src.main
```

## Run tests

```bash
pytest
```
